    - the balance of the address of this contract will be updated to (the balance of the address of this contract-((250*the ether just received (i.e., msg.value))/0xde0b6b3a7640000)).
  - When ((250*the ether just received (i.e., msg.value))/0xde0b6b3a7640000) is greater than the balance of the address of this contract:
    - it transfers (the ether just received (i.e., msg.value)-((the balance of the address of this contract*0xde0b6b3a7640000)/250)) to caller.

      - the balance of the address of this contract will be updated to (the balance of the address of this contract-the balance of the address of this contract).
